      "writtenOn": "2017-09-22T23:18:27Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "ah, is the LUCI_CONTEXT support in a subsequent CL then? Should this be \"\" instead then, since we can\u0027t tell for sure if the token has an email or not?",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 166,
        "startChar": 18,
